keyMappings:
unmapAll

# Navigating the page
map j scrollDown
map k scrollUp
map gg scrollToTop
map G scrollToBottom
map h scrollLeft
map l scrollRight
map s reload
map yy copyCurrentUrl
map p openCopiedUrlInNewTab
map P openCopiedUrlInCurrentTab
map v enterVisualMode
map i LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map I LinkHints.activateMode
map [[ goPrevious
map ]] goNext

# Using the vomnibar
map o Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
map O Vomnibar.activate
map b Vomnibar.activateBookmarksInNewTab
map B Vomnibar.activateBookmarks

# Using find
map / enterFindMode
map n performFind
map N performBackwardsFind

# Navigating history
map r goBack
map u goForward

# Manipulating tabs
map t createTab
map d previousTab
map f nextTab
map x removeTab

# Miscellaneous
map ? showHelp
